<?xml version="1.0" ?>
<!-- FR3 URDF generated by Robot._build_robot_meta() on Positronic Robotics owned Franka arm.

     _build_robot_meta takes the libfranka URDF (which uses package:// URIs for .dae visual
     and .stl collision meshes), rewrites collision refs to bare filenames matching the bundled
     STLs in positronic/assets/fr3_collision/, strips .dae visuals (not bundled), and adds
     <visual> elements for links that lack them. The end_effector link encodes F_T_EE from
     franka::RobotState so the URDF matches the full kinematic chain used by the driver's IK.

     This file must match Robot._build_robot_meta() output exactly (modulo this header).
     Used by cfg.ds.internal as REAL_URDF for backfilling old datasets without robot_meta. -->
